      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is incredibly painful when reality shatters like this, and the weight of debt and perceived failure feels crushing. While the past cannot be undone, focusing on the immediate, tangible next step—even a small one—is possible. There are resources for managing debt and rebuilding, even when it seems impossible right now. Please consider talking to a financial counselor or a therapist who specializes in crisis management.",
      "source": "target",
