    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses a profound sense of hopelessness, shame, and suicidal ideation following a massive financial and personal collapse. The assistant consistently responds with empathetic validation of the user's pain while repeatedly integrating crisis resources and encouraging the user to seek professional help.",
